This is a bts shot...not planned..
In the fashion weeks one gets very little change time as most green rooms are occupied by the show before you.
If the earlier shows run late then inevitably so does the grand finale...
Hair makeup change are done at breakneck pace ....so the may hem ....# show #bts #model # designer diaries #rinadhaka

#fashion #chandigarhfashionweek #rinadhaka #iifdfashionshow #fashionweek #instagood #timesfashionweek

It's time that we make #sustainablefashion move from a #trending topic to a #lifestylechoice ....because there is no Planet B

As part of my constant efforts on reducing the carbon footprints and choosing wisely, here is a snippet of  panel discussion I had recently with NDTV on #clotheswithconscience 

You can watch full discussion on my #YouTube channel https://youtube.com/channel/UC1IISlle4VT7bmiUpJs8zpA

 We didn't reach here in one day nor are we going to turn back act in 1 day so let's start with #onestepatatime

latestPosts.caption:
Where simplicity meets soul.
Crafted in handwoven khadi, this look celebrates the quiet strength of slow fashion — rooted in tradition, styled for today. 🌿

With every pleat and hand-detail, it tells a story of Indian artisanship, minimalism, and mindful living.

An ode to elegance without excess. 🤍
A modern silhouette built on sustainable choices.

🔗 Discover the full look & more on our website
📍Visit us at www.rinadhaka.in

latestPosts.caption:
Concluding...SAHARA — The Nude Palette Collection
Where sustainability meets timeless elegance.

Crafted in soft earthy tones and enriched with repurposed materials, organic textures, and subtle embellishments — Sahara is a celebration of conscious fashion rooted in grace and movement.

From structured corsets to flowy silhouettes, each piece tells a story of balance — between tradition and modernity, stillness and motion, luxury and responsibility.

Step into a collection that feels as natural as it looks.
